metadata.name: Amaya
metadata.description:
Amaya had woken up in the middle of the night..
A sudden urge to take action awoke in her..
As if there were parts in her head that were not in place..
and she remembered that she had a mission..
She was time to hit the road..
She was one of those holy eyes..
